You can change the background color of a label by setting it as a UIColor, like you would do with shapes.

image::labelBackgroundColor/labelBackgroundColor.png["Label Background Color",height=500]

Background Color
----------------
The backgroundColor property of a C4Label can be set like so:

[source]
----
label.backgroundColor = C4BLUE;
----